Requirements: 

if u haven't seen a system, you can have a rough flow of the system, 
make sure you don't waste too much time here and just select 5-7 steps.

 - User selects a city and see list of movies, 
 - then selects a movie and see lists of theatre then he clicks a theatre and see show timings, 
 - then he clicks on show timings and see the seatmap. 
 - in the seat map he can select a seat where concurrent requests can come. 
 - then he does the payment and gets a ticket.

entities:
 - user
 - city
 - movies
 - theatres
 - shows
 - seatmap for theatre
 - tickets

service functions:
 - select city
 - see list of movies
 - select a movie and see list of theatres.
 - select a theatre and see shows timings.
 - select a show and see seatmap.
 - select a seat in seatmap.
 - do the payment and get a ticket

think about design patterns: 
 - 
